  "text": "All subjects underwent a standardized MRI imaging protocol at 3.0 Tesla that included a 3D magnetization prepared rapid acquisition gradient echo (MPRAGE) sequence. All images underwent pre-processing that included corrections for gradient non-linearity [CITATION_1] and intensity inhomogeneity using both the N3 bias correction [CITATION_2] followed by the SPM5-based bias correction.",
